General.Name: Cint Group AB
General.Description: Cint Group AB (publ) provides software solutions for digital insights gathering worldwide. The company's products portfolio includes Access by Cint, a bidding and ordering tool for seeking consumer insights in open marketplace; Access Pro by Cint, a full insights management tool that enables users to achieve complex and sophisticated sample configurations by combining the open marketplace with ad-hoc and in-house panels; and Access Enterprise by Cint, a sample management platform that provides access to business intelligence data to obtain insights and operate research and sample management. It also provides Track by Cint, a management tool to track brand development and loyalty; Connect by Cint, an audience insights tool to identify and analyze including online advertising and content, as well as impact of marketing campaigns; and Engage by Cint, which connects supply partners with its B2B customers through the company's software platform. In addition, the company offers On-Time-Supply API, which provides near real-time respondent data to enable suppliers to send respondents into the Lucid marketplace; and Over-The-Counter, a method of delivery that connects buyers to audiences that are traditionally harder to reach. It also provides media measurement products, which includes impact measurement, impact measurement API, and custom media measurement; data solution products, such as data collaboration and data licensing. Further, the company offers market research and insights, audience monetization, advertising and media campaign measurement, and enterprise solutions. Cint Group AB (publ) was incorporated in 1998 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
